tem_usage_rate\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate high usage causing potential service degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate normal median: 25.2, fault median: 67.73, change_ratio: 0.9152\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased significantly during the fault\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max normal p99: 7421.59, fault p99: 17279.32, change_ratio: 0.7982\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max showed notable increment during the fault\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max normal p99: 84118.33, fault p99: 84767.32, change_ratio: 0.0077\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n以上 JSON 格式从异常指标中提取了关键组件和可能的故障原因，供后续深入分析和解决。", "trace_analysis_findings": "我已经分析了异常期间的 `Trace` 数据，以下是初步找到的重要信息和异常行为的提取结果。\n\n### 初步分析发现（全面扫描完成）\n1. 总共发现了16个显著异常调用链。\n2. 异常集中在高延迟和错误传播方面。\n3. 多个核心服务，如 `cartservice`、`checkoutservice` 和 `shippingservice` 出现延迟暴增现象。\n4. 最大的延迟放大倍数超过一般范围 10 倍以上，特别是在 `Redis` 和 `Shipping` 服务之间。\n\n### JSON 格式输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant delay observed during anomalies, particularly for the `cartservice` making calls to `redis`.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal Avg Duration: 1573ms, Anomaly Avg Duration: 9442ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Massive latency increase observed from `checkoutservice` when calling shipping methods.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Relation: `checkoutservice -> shippingservice`. Normal Avg Duration: ~14000ms, Anomaly Avg Duration: ~75000+ms.\"\n    },\n 